➜江西诗人时差先生：尘埃
http://www.sohu.com/a/421480970_100115135	45620
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20200928/48f15ef8570a4061b1ad86eba04e6d55.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>尘埃</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>文/时差先生</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">一个个尘埃</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">飘起落下，落下又飘起</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">只有风读懂它生命的定力</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">太过渺小，太过卑微</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">却能反射阳光</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">给远方一片蓝色光明</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">万物皆有灵，独何以栖身</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">待尘埃落定</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">但褪去浮世光华</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">隐喻万般重生</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">一只木鱼被人敲起</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">声音笃笃，旋律单调</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">如尘埃的方向</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">不知划去了多少凡世往事</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">有些人对尘埃视而不见</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">看不见它的高度</p>            <div class="lookall-box">
<div class="lookall-shadow"></div>
